description.submission: Submit a link to the landing page of your Web application running on Netlify.
description.landing_page: The landing page should include the following:
items: Your full name and section
Links to each of the lab assignments
Link to the Kanbas application
Links to all relevant source code repositories
description.requirement: The Kanabas application should include a link to navigate back to the landing page.
